Official Notice
As a member of the Official Board, not of the Church but of
the Club, I want to call attention to the article in the "Discipline"
that urges everyone to be a myobist in religion. The collection
taken up after the last course will be turned over to the
"Stewards," not of the Church but of the Club. The supper will
be over in time to permit sons to attend church.-J. M. LEE.
